---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---
<footer class="border-t border-line mt-0" style="background: var(--color-bg-dark); color: var(--color-fg-inv);">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-16 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 text-sm">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display italic text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--color-fg-inv);">Emilie Pruneta</p>
      <p style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.55); line-height: 1.7;">
        Photographe de mariage et de famille en Corrèze.<br/>
        Reportages naturels et émotionnels depuis 2012.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.4);">Prestations</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2" style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.65);">
        <li><a href="#mariages" class="hover:text-bg transition-colors">Mariage</a></li>
        <li><a href="#famille" class="hover:text-bg transition-colors">Famille</a></li>
        <li><a href="#famille" class="hover:text-bg transition-colors">Grossesse</a></li>
        <li><a href="#famille" class="hover:text-bg transition-colors">Nouveau-né</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.4);">Contact</p>
      <p style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.65);">Corrèze · Lot · Dordogne<br/>et toute la France pour les mariages</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
        Prendre contact <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t" style="border-color: rgba(250,248,245,0.08);">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs" style="color: rgba(250,248,245,0.35);">
      <p>&copy; {year} Emilie Pruneta · Photographe</p>
      <p>Site réalisé par <a href="https://veridian.site" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-bg transition-colors" style="color:rgba(250,248,245,0.5);">Veridian</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
